    "v2": "&#39;Tis Christ that wrought this work for me, My faithful Savior, Whom Thou hast made mine eyes to see By Thy favor. Now I know He is my Life, My Help in need and dying.",
    "v3": "Him Thou hast unto all set forth Their great Salvation And to His kingdom called the earth, Every nation, By Thy dear and wholesome Word, In every place resounding.",
    "v4": "He is the Hope and saving Light Of lands benighted; By Him are they who dwelt in night Fed and lighted. He is Israel&#39;s Praise and Bliss, Their Joy, Reward, and Glory."
  },
